<div class="jumbotron">
  <h1 class="title">招聘网</h1>
  <p class="slogan">
  我们希望藉由这个网站，能让大家找到且应征上高薪且优质的工作。
  <br>
   凭借自己的努力和天份也会变 Winner
  </p>
  <p class="lead"><a class="btn btn-lg btn-danger" href="/jobs">马上应征</a></p>
</div>


  <section id="liucheng">
    <div class = "container">
      <div class = "row">

        <div class="col-sm-3">
          <div class="thumbnail">
            <img src='<%= image_url 'human-resources.png' %>' alt="筛选职位" class = "img-thhumbnail">
            <div class="caption">
              <h3>筛选职位</h3>
              <p>根据自身情况，选择适合自已的工作</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>


        <div class="col-sm-3">
          <div class="thumbnail">
            <img src='<%= image_url 'curriculum.png' %>' alt="投递简历" class = "img-thhumbnail">
            <div class="caption">
              <h3>投递简历</h3>
              <p>在线投递自己的简历，认真写好的简历可以提升录取机率</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>


        <div class="col-sm-3">
          <div class="thumbnail">
            <img src='<%= image_url 'chat.png' %>' alt="邀请面试" class = "img-thhumbnail">
            <div class="caption">
              <h3>邀请面试</h3>
              <p>公司接受到您的简历，会向您发出面试邀请。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>


        <div class="col-sm-3">
          <div class="thumbnail">
            <img src='<%= image_url 'job.png' %>' alt="上班工作" class = "img-thhumbnail">
            <div class="caption">
              <h3>上班工作</h3>
              <p>面试通过后，就可以上岗工作了。祝您工作顺利！</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
